 Block comments
+-----------------+-----------------+-----+-----------------+------------------------+
| comment(ns)::U  |                 |     | ibase=$indent+1 | :first:ws              |
:                 :                 :     : ipar=$indent    :                        :
+-----------------+-----------------+-----+-----------------+------------------------+
| :first:ws       | [ \t]           | >>  | ibase += 1      | :first:ws              |
| :first:ws       | [\n]            | >>  |                 | :nl                    |
| :first:ws       | .               | >>a |                 | :data                  |
+-----------------+-----------------+-----+----------------+-------------------------+
| :data           | [\n]            | >>  | a>>s            | :nl                    |
| :data           | .               | >>a |                 | :data                  |
+-----------------+-----------------+-----+----------------+-------------------------+
| :nl             | {$indent>ibase} |     |                 | :data                  |
| :nl             | [ \t]           | >>  |                 | :nl                    |
| :nl             | [\n]            | >>a | a>>s            | :nl                    |
| :nl             | {$indent<=ipar} |     | s>>p            | <ns>                   |
| :nl             | .               | >>a | ibase=$indent   | :data                  |
+-----------------+-----------------+-----+----------------+-------------------------+
| {eof}           |                 |     | a>>s; s>>p      | <ns>                   |
+-----------------+-----------------+-----+-----------------+------------------------+
